include ../../mixins/_iconLink

section.about#about
  .section-container.pt-lg.pb-lg
    .title-container.mb-md
      span.section-title about me
    .about__content
      .about__portrait
        div
          span(class='about__img', role='img', aria-label='Portrait of Michael Michelotti')
        .about__links
          +iconLink('about', githubLink, 'github')
          +iconLink('about', resumeLink, 'resume')
          +iconLink('about', linkedinLink, 'linkedin')
      .about__text
        p.about__p
          | I have a Bachelor's degree in Physics from the University of Maryland, College Park. Since graduating, my interest has veered towards Computer Engineering and Computer Science.
        p.about__p
          | Since 2020, I have been teaching myself the fundamentals of Computer Science: processor architecture, code compilation, communication protocols. Today, I specialize in embedded systems software.
          | In my free time, I build embedded projects utilizing ARM Cortex-M processors from various vendors, especially ST. I also often use powerful frameworks such as ESP-IDF and FreeRTOS.
          | I'm interested in data science; at my current job I created a Python data pipeline for processing sensor data collected by a drone.
        p.about__p
          | I am currently building a dynamic hot-pluggable WS2812 LED grid and a sensor mesh that measures air parameters in my apartment.
          | Lastly, I'm keeping my web design skills sharp by maintaining this website.
